                {gettext("Bulk Task Creation with Nested Goals")}
              </h4>

              <div class="mb-4">
                <h5 class="font-semibold text-base-content mb-2">
                  <strong>POST /api/tasks with nested tasks</strong>
                </h5>
                <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 mb-2">
                  {gettext("Create a goal with multiple child tasks in a single atomic API call:")}
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-base-content opacity-70">
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Atomic transactions")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Uses Ecto.Multi to ensure all-or-nothing semantics (if any task fails, entire operation rolls back)")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Automatic parent_id assignment")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Child tasks automatically linked to parent goal")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Automatic identifier generation")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Goals get G prefix (G1, G2, etc.), tasks get W/D prefix based on type")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Position management")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Goal positioned first, child tasks positioned sequentially after")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Task history tracking")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Creation history entries created for goal and all child tasks")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("PubSub broadcasting")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Real-time updates broadcast for goal and all children")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Telemetry events")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - [:kanban, :goal, :created_with_tasks] event emitted with goal and task counts")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("WIP limit enforcement")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Respects column WIP limits before creating goal")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Full field support")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Preserves all AI-optimized fields (complexity, verification_steps, key_files, etc.)")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Response format")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Returns {goal: ..., child_tasks: [...]} with complete task data")}
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-3">
                {gettext("Automatic Goal Deletion")}
              </h4>

              <div class="mb-4">
                <h5 class="font-semibold text-base-content mb-2">
                  {gettext("Smart goal cleanup")}
                </h5>
                <p class="text-base-content opacity-70 mb-2">
                  {gettext("Goals are automatically deleted when all their child tasks are removed:")}
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-base-content opacity-70">
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Cascade deletion")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - When the last child task of a goal is deleted, the parent goal is automatically deleted as well")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Real-time updates")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Goal deletion broadcasts via PubSub for immediate UI updates")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Prevents orphaned goals")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Ensures goals without children don't remain on the board")}
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>{gettext("Proper reordering")}</strong>
                    {gettext(" - Tasks are reordered after goal deletion to maintain proper positioning")}
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
